1) In ERF,make sure to first do "git submodule --init --recursive" to make sure you 
checkout the ekat repo, and all the repos included from ekat.

2) You will need to build and install the kokkos library which is inside Submodules/ekat.

From Submodules/ekat/extern/kokkos, type

mkdir build
cd build
cmake ../  -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=g++ -DKokkos_ROOT=../install

3) Somewhere other than in ERF, let's call it WORK_DIR, type

git clone git@github.com:E3SM-Project/E3SM.git

4) In ERF/external, type

ln -s WORK_DIR/E3SM/components/eamxx/src/physics/shoc/  shoc

5) In ERF/Exec/DevTests/Shoc, type

make



